title: (SOLVED) 820-3476 no power
message:
Does it turn on with charger alone?
Post PPBUS_G3H voltage in this case.
If still no good, check diode mode to ground.

title: (SOLVED) 820-3476 no power
message:
Be sure F7140 is good.
Post U7100 basic voltages; pins 1, 2, 3, 9, 12, 13, 14, 15, 17, 19, 20, 27.
